data.description: A rare find in the lovely neighborhood of Abington. This gorgeous custom built home boasts 4 BR, 2½ BA and a spacious floor plan that allows for a harmonious flow. The entire home has beautiful warm wood cabinetry and warm wood trim throughout. Kitchen has elegant granite countertops and tile backsplash with a work triangle set up for maximum efficiency. Breakfast room opens to a massive back deck that is perfect for entertaining.   Home is located in close proximity to downtown Kernersville and provides quick access to Greensboro & Winston Salem.  PTI minutes away.   Home has 2 wood burning masonry fireplaces, Flex Room on lower level would be perfect as movie room, game room or convert to guest quarters. Multi-purpose/office has its own private entry. Both rooms in basement have HVAC vents. Home has new carpet & has been professionally painted. Tons of    storage. No HOA fee! This home is full of space allowing functionality and flexibility. Call today to schedule an appointment.
